                  Resource (.arxml) that defines this vendor specific module definition.
               </documentation>
               <appinfo>
                  <meta.attribute kind="resource"/>
               </appinfo>
            </annotation>
         </attribute>
         <attribute name="requiredMcus" type="string">
            <annotation>
               <documentation>
                  A comma separated list of MCU names that this module supports. For example MPC551x,MPC5567. If the module has no hardware dependencies this field is left blank.
               </documentation>
            </annotation>
         </attribute>
         <attribute name="version" type="string">
            <annotation>
               <documentation>
                  
               </documentation>
            </annotation>
         </attribute>
         <attribute name="imageIdentifier" type="string" use="required">
            <annotation>
               <documentation>
                  A small image representing this module definition.
